aa(lp261
VSo, if teasing unnecessary suffering out of the system was our first design cue,
p262
aVthen tending to dignity by way of the senses,
p263
aVby way of the body \u2014 the aesthetic realm \u2014
p264
aVis design cue number two.
p265
aVNow this gets us quickly to the third and final bit for today;
p266
aVnamely, we need to lift our sights, to set our sights on well-being,
p267
aVso that life and health and healthcare
p268
aVcan become about making life more wonderful,
p269
aVrather than just less horrible.
p270
aVBeneficence.
